data.description: Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 4 bathroom residence that seamlessly blends elegance with modern comfort. As you enter, you are greeted by a spacious foyer that leads to the heart of the home. The open floor plan effortlessly connects the kitchen to the inviting living area, creating a perfect space for entertaining friends and family. The well-appointed kitchen features state-of-the-art appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space, making it a culinary haven for both aspiring and seasoned chefs. Zoned to the CCISD.     Do not wait. Book your tour today!!
